doctype
html
  head
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    title 1batch
    link(rel="stylesheet", type="text/css", href="lib/bootstrap.min.css")
  body
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h1 1batch is an app for sharing 8 photos.
      .row
        .col-sm-12.col-md-6
          h3 Publish one batch of photos
          p 📷 Take as much time as you need to pick the perfect set, then publish them all at once.
          p 🌟 Follow your friends and help them pick their top photos.
        .col-sm-12.col-md-6
          h3 Keep your photos for 6 months
          p 📱 Post comments and updates (your friend finished their project! Bill got engaged!).
          p ⏰ Don't add any new photos for 6 months.
          p 💔 You can always hide or delete a photo if it's no longer relevant.
      .row
        .col-sm-12.col-md-4
        .col-sm-12.col-md-4
        .col-sm-12.col-md-4
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h2 what can you say in 8 photos?
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h3 Open Source Software
          h4 💻 1batch is open source
          p That means coders can add on to it, or make their own apps. And anyone can code, so that new app might be yours!
          p
            span Check out our&nbsp;
            a(href="https://github.com/mapmeld/1batch") GitHub project
            span &nbsp;and&nbsp;
            a(href="#") Getting Started
            span &nbsp;page.
